            Force = true,

        var membership = new AliCloud.Ram.GroupMembership("membership", new AliCloud.Ram.GroupMembershipArgs
        {
            GroupName = @group.Name,
            UserNames =

            },
        });

    </dt>

            title="Optional">
        <span id="state_usernames_csharp">

</span>

    </dt>

{{% /md %}}</dd>
</dl>

## Import


RAM Group membership can be imported using the id, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import alicloud:ram/groupMembership:GroupMembership example my-group
```
